!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Welcome to our newsletter</title>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<style type="text/css">
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #f1f1f1;
			padding: 20px;
			line-height: 1.5;
			color: #333;
		}
		h1, h2, h3, p {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}
		h1 {
			font-size: 36px;
			font-weight: bold;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}
		h2 {
			font-size: 28px;
			font-weight: bold;
			margin-bottom: 15px;
		}
		hr {
			border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
			margin: 30px 0;
		}
		.container {
			background-color: #fff;
			padding: 40px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}
		.btn {
			display: inline-block;
			background-color: #4CAF50;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			text-decoration: none;
			margin: 20px 0 40px;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Welcome to our newsletter</h1>
		<p>Dear {{username}},</p>
		<p>We're happy to have you as a subscriber to our newsletter. Here are some updates and news for you:</p>
		{{!-- <h2>{{title1}}</h2>
		<p>{{description1}}</p> --}}
		<hr>
		{{!-- <h2>{{title2}}</h2>
		<p>{{description2}}</p> --}}
		<p>Thank you for reading our newsletter. If you have any questions or feedback, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
		<a href="{{authUrl}}{{email}}/{{code}}" class="btn">click me to verification</a>
	</div>
</body>
</html>